auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>After 18 and 11 months, we just lost Mack Intosh Ulysses Cat aka Scuppermog.
He was the bestest, friendliest, most unflappable boi. Vets loved him, dogs loved him, he came when called or whistled, sat, shook hand and begged on command and gave us all of his heart every day of the sixteen years he shared with us in four homes and two states.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eCPQYMq.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sorry for the potato quality, this video is super old.  He was a player as a young cat.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/d70jIrI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Oldest photo we have of him. Hard to tell, but he was much smaller then.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1tkiWc3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A bit of a chonk in his sweater. Expression says it all.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Te2EOMx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PCp1Zhs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>There may have nip involved as a bribe here</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CFkH4gr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And yes, he played for the Bears.  True story /s</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VpTQ863.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Mack modeling Lolita headgear</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/roR1AC5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Christmas photo.  Happy reindeer family</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JEujiZK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>unflappable</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tRs0y6S.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6bCmLLs.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>First reaction to Roomba</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RmvL6ip.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A week later</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/K4HR4V5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He loved naps, especially in the sun</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8yfiLKs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/G7Gz9ue.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/J0SfRva.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/crSuOsd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QH07wkj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/04bNOUb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UxpfnKo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XrR6AgH.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Also loved food. Squeeze treats, popcorn, caviar, salmon and turkey dinner.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/u21wpxh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This was his chonky phase. That we know of, he ate the caramel topping off an entire bundt cake, half a bag of tortilla chips, a quarter loaf of bread, half a bag of shredded cheese, and spicy soaking pan water when he was not supposed to.
One morning he managed to pull several cans of wet cat food out of the upper cabinets ninja style.
He also cost us an apartment deposit by pushing over a seriously heavy cake dome intended to keep him out and broke a tile.
We ended up putting child locks on everything to get him dechonked.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QWCN84n.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He saw us at our less than best, and loved us anyway</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PlnEFn5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sorry for the selfie, but this says a lot about who Mack was.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Qa8w6Dt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He was leash trained, and loved going for walks. Here he is, throwing up from too much grass. My wife royally pissed off the lawn obsessed neighbor by refusing to treat the grass, because she knew Mack liked to eat it.  Up yours Chuck.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/m4aqVu9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Every time Tank (the pittie) got a bath, Mack had to try to save him from the dog and cat melting solvent, AKA shower water.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HZQfPGr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is how pretty he was, when he wanted to be.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/g9cnKJ4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Christmas 2021, in his present.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oYsAgig.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is what he would do during remote work meetings.

Thank you for reading, just wanted people to know he existed, and was a really good cat.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/05YIGQO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Wonkable]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Love Tim Curry</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vBjn4x9</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hLfg9JU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vBjn4x9</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sunday Dump(ster)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/1jv0eI3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KGGmp9W.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/1jv0eI3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[funkystay]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Rich entitled shithead has a racist meltdown over a smoothie</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Au7yn10</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HV6jVoJ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RnYrOp5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Au7yn10</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AoShin]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Gonna have to dump right here.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NOKimrY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hQr1gE3.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tjFBTD6.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7M3XZci.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yEA98pj.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><s